query:
SELECT 
  SUBSTRING(partNumber, 1, 10) as part_prefix,
  COUNT(*) as count,
  MIN(name) as sample_name
FROM products 
WHERE brand = 'Agilent'
GROUP BY SUBSTRING(partNumber, 1, 10)
ORDER BY count DESC
LIMIT 20
